            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1= @page_sub_title = "Item Enchantments"
                %p
                    Enchantments must be referenced by their Bukkit name in the XML. Bukkit names will always be uppercase with underscores for spaces, capitalization and underscores don't matter in the XML.
                %p
                    %code NOTE:
                    PGM allows enchantments to be applied to any item regardless if the enchant was intended for it or not.
                %br

